via the steep south pillar route because none of our 
countrymen has ever done it in the past said team leader choi 
changmin of seoul 
although the south pillar route is the most direct path to the 
top of everest only two men one from poland and another from 
czechoslovakia have succeeded in climbing it 
from lukla the 20man team hopes to reach khumbu glacier their 
planned base camp by aug 26 the olympics are to begin in seoul 
south korea on sept 17 
