second expedition to do so following a swiss team in 1956 
but they the swiss did not climb the two peaks on the same 
day we will try on the same day said nam sunwu the teams 
climbing leader 
ko sangdon the first korean to scale everest reached the peak 
in 1977 last year heo youngho became the second korean to 
