mccain rariz 
this is one of those times when you cant reach bipartisan 
consensus dole told the senate 
noting that many of those voting for the democratic plan have 
opposed contra aid in the past dole said there are some of us 
on this side of the aisle who look at some of those who are about 
to vote for contra aid with disbelief and skepticism 
accusing the democrats of using their contraaid plan as a big 
umbrella political cover in this presidential election year 
