<TEXT>
in the early morning hours after northwest flight 
255 crashed and exploded on a highway last summer a graybearded 
man with a clerical collar was there to comfort relatives of the 
156 victims 
one of those relatives had a brother who was a roman catholic 
priest and something seemed wrong father john irish withdrew 
